    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "They provide good online lectures and helps us understand everything as they provide recorded lectures as well.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is also a virtual ai which will help you anytime. They provide feedback classes as well and doubt sessions too.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The best part is you can choose exam slot according to your schedule which i liked the most, so that you can manage it well.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "the faculty and the teaching methods are also good and they do their work nicely",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "they ensures the placement also and provide internships for each student who are eligible",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Study material is relevant and up to date and is relevant in todays time",
          "name": "Bhavyansh Sharma",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure- Good facilities for events and occasional visits well maintained campus. In online degree you will visit college once or twice a year but the experience you will get will be amazing for sure.",
          "name": "KUSHAGRA BAJAJ",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I have a mentor which keeps me updated about assignments",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placements are also given from 2nd semester.",
          "name": "Hardik singh kalsi",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Easy assignments to complete and topics divided into modules",
          "name": "Arman shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "there should be more subject added realted to my course so it helps us in personal development also",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "if the teacher gives us some work or modules to complete then they have to check it otherwise the student didn't take much interest in doing it",
          "name": "Shreya",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Too many certificate course mandatory for students",
          "name": "Bhavyansh Sharma",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement Support- Average career advancement support could be better.",
          "name": "KUSHAGRA BAJAJ",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The re-exam and re-assignment fees are much than the other colleges like manipal online or Graphic era online they charges are very high money I have missed exam due to their technical glitch for that I had paid 1000 to attempt exam again.",
          "name": "KUSHAGRA BAJAJ",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The timetable is not that organized.Some classes are on monday and some on Saturday.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "We cannot get in touch with the teachers personally by getting their contacts",
          "name": "Hardik singh kalsi",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lecture Quality is not up to the mark, it’s subjective.",
          "name": "Ashish Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Limited Social Iteraction: While online format provides flexibility, it lacks the vibrant campus life and face-to-face interactions found in traditional universities.",
          "name": "Kartik",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fee Increases and Transparency Issues: There have been complaints about annual fee hikes, with some students feeling like that these increases are not communicated clearly during enrollement",
          "name": "Kartik",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        }
      ]
    }
